Multiprocess Commmunication Library
===================================

The multiprocess communication library (a.k.a MCL) provides software for
developing low-latency message-passing systems. Message-passing is performed
using IPv6 multicast.

Installation
------------

The package can be installed using::

    sudo pip install .

Support
------------

If you find a bug, please report the issue to::

    a.bender@acfr.usyd.edu.au
